speaker: Ty
text: Hi Na! Have you got gifts for your family yet?

speaker: Na
text: No, I have no idea what to get my sisters

speaker: Ty
text: How many sisters do you have?

speaker: Na
text: I have two older sisters and one younger sister

speaker: Ty
text: Why don’t you get them some key chains?

speaker: Na
text: That sounds good. And now something for my younger brother

speaker: Ty
text: You have a big family! How old is your younger brother?

speaker: Na
text: His name is Teo. He’s very mischievous.

speaker: Ty
text: Yeah, you’re all the same. Haha.
